Use this workflow to update a tag in your CD repo. 

Parameters ~ 

NEW_IMAGE ~ Name of the image to update 
NEW_TAG ~ New tag for the image 
DEPLOYMENT_FILE ~ Name of deployment file 
CONTAINER_NAME ~ Name of container of the image to update 
COMMITER_EMAIL ~ Email address of commiter 
GIT_USER ~ Username of commiter 
BRANCH ~ Branch to push changes to 
REPO_OWNER ~ Own
REPO_NAME ~ Name of repo to update 
